<br>
Also, if you are considering group power of Dire Charm, the DS of the epic and hps of the mob are irrelevant.<br>
<br>
If you are considering solo power, the DS and hps are very relevant.<br>
<br>
Two separate tests are required: pet vs dire charm solo.  pet vs. dire charm in exp groups.<br>
<br>
Also, a dire charm pet should be compared against straight Greater Vocerates ... it should not exceed their power either.<br>
<br>
Someone else can run these tests.  I can't muster the energy to prove the obvious to myself, nor do I know any enchanters/necros with the skill.<br>
